name: ETHETF
description: ETHETF Token is a speculative ERC-20 token which follows and celebrates the progress around the first Ethereum ETF approval and gives crypto enthusiats the chance to earn rewards from a real-life event. The token is launched as a fair launch with no presale stages. The token has an initial 2% buy tax which is automatically burnt to support and reward community's commitment. This buy tax will be eliminated after the approval of the first spot Ethereum ETF to celebrate this milestone.
